    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine example of the A80 chassis, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six. This unit retains its factory-spec sequential ceramic turbos and the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The drivetrain is mechanically flawless, with no signs of heat cycling on the vacuum lines or boost leaks in the intercooler piping. The rear end is equipped with the original Torsen limited-slip differential, and the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension remains tight, providing exceptional lateral grip. Finished in showroom-quality paint with a perfectly preserved interior, this vehicle represents a true collector-grade specimen with zero aftermarket modifications to the ECU or forced induction system.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
